**/_build_out/
**/_build_out_svc/

# Local / heavy datasets (LabelMe, archives) — keep out of Git LFS unless intended
dataset/
dataset.rar

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Configuration: tracked vs ignored (explicit)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# TRACKED (do not add ignore rules for these):
#   - appsettings.json (base config; placeholders OK)
#   - **/Properties/launchSettings.json (see negation below — never ignore)
#
# IGNORED (local / secrets):
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/appsettings.*.local.json
**/secrets.json

# Re-include template next to ignored Development file (explicit; basename differs anyway).
!**/appsettings.Development.json.example

# Never ignore launch profiles (URLs, env for local run) — explicit allow.
!**/Properties/launchSettings.json
_build_*/

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Local-only / không đưa lên GitHub (điều chỉnh nếu team muốn track README hoặc docs)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
/README.md
SP26SE110_BoneVisQA/README.md
SP26SE110_BoneVisQA/.cursorrules
SP26SE110_BoneVisQA/docs/**/*.md
.postman/

# Postman globals cục bộ (thường chứa biến môi trường); collection trong repo có thể add tay
postman/globals/
